manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Question: Bubbles are generated after installation? Answer: If bubbles appear, try using a bank card or a card with a harder edge and gently push it along the film. When using hard-edged cards, you need to wrap them with a thin cloth pad to avoid scratching the protective film. Question: How to avoid dust spots? Answer: Wet paper towels, dry paper towels and dust removal stickers are included in the box to help you install the screen protector. Before placing the screen protector, follow the instructions in the package to clean the screen. Before using the screen protector, make sure that there is no dirt or dust on the screen. Question ：Will it be difficult to install a mobile phone screen protector? Answer： Every customer who buys a product in KATIN will get an instruction manual on how to install the screen protector, which is accompanied by a very intuitive and detailed video. If you have any problems during the installation process, you can let us help you. Question ：The product is cracked or the model is wrong after receiving it? Answer：When you get a broken product, it may be caused by a large squeeze or impact during the long-term transportation. When you receive the wrong product, it may be that the warehouse receives a large amount of goods and the product is in confusion during sorting. Don't worry, Please contact Amazon service in time or get in touch with us via Amazon email following steps: Go to Your Orders, find your order in the list, and click Problem with order. and the problem will be solved well for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nicer than most
reviews.reviewText: It came with 2 cover glasses, and 2 sets of the typical installation aids: wet wipe, dry wipe, and dust removal sticker. I used them all in about 2 minutes, then set it on the phone, and it fit great, and looks nice. If you open the box carefully, it hinges open, and is convenient for storing the 2nd glass, in case you don't have 2 identical phones. Also, it tells all about the lifetime warranty: they say you can contact them anytime if it breaks, or you otherwise become dissatisfied with it. (I didn't test this.)Also, it includes a URL and QR code to a short YouTube video showing how to install it for best results, recommended if you haven't done it before, or if you want better results than last time.
